    <item>
      <title>HHKBをWindows・Mac・iPadで快適に使う方法</title>
      <link>https://www.meganii.com/blog/2021/01/15/how-to-set-up-hhkb-to-switch-comfortably-between-win-mac-and-ipad/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Jan 2021 06:35:29 +0900</pubDate>
      
